snippet.title: Watch Dogs 2 - Zodiac Killer Mission - Pre-order Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out Watch Dogs 2 at http://www.watchdogs.com

Pre-order now and get access to the Zodiac Killer extra mission. A killer is staging the bodies of his victims all over Oakland and taunting the police like the infamous Zodiac Killer of the Sixties. Decrypt the messages and hunt down the copycat!
